Beginner

Task 1: Basic Task

1 - ls 
2 - mkdir myProject
3 - cd myProject
4 - touch app.js
5 - cd Desktop
6 - mkdir myProject2
7 - cp app.js /myProject2

Task 2: Absolute and Relative Paths

1 - touch exercise.txt 
2 - rm /exercise.txt

Intermediate

Task 3: Cat commands 

1 - cd myProject 
2 - touch umuzi.txt recruits.txt cohort.txt
3 - ls 
4 - nano umuzi.txt
5 - ctrl x 
6 - y and enter
7 - nano recruits.txt 
8 - ctrl x
9 - y and enter
10- nano cohort.txt
11- ctrl x
12- y and enter
13- cat umuzi.txt
14- cat recruit.txt
15- cat cohort.txt
16- touch summary.txt
17- cat umuzi.txt recruits.txt cohort.txt > summary.txt 

Task 4: The locate command 
1 - locate umuzi
2 - search umuzi >> search_result.txt

Task 5: The loacate command cont..
1 -mkdir mydocuments 
2 - cd mydocuments
3 - touch pad.txt
4 - cd ../..
5 - cd Desktop
6 - loacate pad_copy.txt

Task 6: Find commands 
1 - find . -type f -name "*.pdf"
2 - find . -type f -name "*.pdf" |tee -a /home/zoe/Desktop/myProject2
3 - find . -daystart -print

Task 10: Text editor 
1 - nano 
2 - mkdir my_files
3 - mv my_bio.txt my_files





